      "Title": "Topic",
      "Type": "Summary"
    },
    {
      "Text": "This update for memcached fixes the following issues\n\n- CVE-2026-47783: timing side-channel in SASL password database authentication (username) (bsc#1265873).\n- CVE-2026-47784: timing side-channel in SASL password database authentication (password) (bsc#1265881).\n",
      "Title": "Details",
      "Type": "General"
